"Charles F. Coghlan (actor born 1896)" 0 Charles Coghlan (December 1, 1896 – March 16, 1972), American actor and writer, he was the son of Charles Francis Coghlan and nephew of Rose Coghlan. His much older sister was stage actress Gertrude Coghlan. Coghlan died in Hershey, Pennsylvania.
